# InfoTrem Submodule Ownership

Agents may always analyze and propose changes for both application submodules:

- `infotrem-web`
- `infotrem-api`

When implementing fixes, features, or improvements, agents may create branches
and open pull requests in either or both submodule repositories when that is the
right scope for the work.

Keep root orchestration changes in the root `infotrem` repository. Keep
frontend and backend implementation changes in their owning submodules unless
the user explicitly asks for a different layout.
